---
// Shared library loader for the educational subject tools (Physics /
// Chemistry / Biology). Emits Three.js (3D) + Chart.js (graphs) from the
// CSP-allowed CDN, then the same-origin shared kit (window.STK).
//
// Order matters: the CDN globals must exist before subject-kit.js runs, and
// STK must exist before any tool's own <script is:inline>. Place this
// component ABOVE the tool's inline script in the page.
---
<script is:inline src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/three.js/r128/three.min.js"></script>
<script is:inline src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/4.4.0/chart.umd.min.js"></script>
<script is:inline src="/subject-kit.js"></script>
